attributes.description: This dashboard provides an overview of macOS unified logs.

params.markdown:
### MacOS
   
#### Description

This dashboard provides visibility into the macOS Unified Logs data stream, offering insights into system and application events across the operating system. It highlights event distribution by message type, event type, and category, enabling users to understand the nature and frequency of system activities. The dashboard presents visual breakdowns of events by subsystem to identify key system components generating logs, along with detailed tables showcasing the top process image paths and top sender image paths for deeper operational context. Together, these visualizations help monitor system behavior, troubleshoot issues, and enhance macOS endpoint visibility.
